                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <p>We’re a group of young students, who created this site to make people realize how important upcycling really is, and how important it is for the environment.</p>
                <p>Upcycling is taking an item that is no longer needed or wanted and giving it new life as something that is either useful or creative. This seemingly basic concept has sparked an exciting revolution with this generation.</p>
                <p>We have together built this community, and we are focusing on showing our visitors what we can do with these materials, to make them realize how so few materials can save more than you can imagine.</p>
                <p>Some people are fascinated about upcycling, how terrible materials can make such beautiful and  useful  creations. It’s all about using  the imagination. That’s why we’re here, we show the world what upcycling can do and what it can create, that’s our goal of this project, and we’re going to fulfill the fact that this can save our world.</p>
